(175, 'Katy through Stephanie''s eyes:\n\nHow do I describe the person that changed my life forever and the person I will spend the rest of my life with?  From the very first moment Katy and I met, I knew that she was "the one".  The first date we ever had, we were completely relaxed with each other - as if we had known each other for a lifetime.  She claims that I am her rock, but she is my sail, that keeps me going at a steady pace, and that with her support through any winds, we can accomplish anything together.\n\nThe first time I saw Katy interact with our nephews, I was mesmerized.  Their reaction to see Aunt Katy, to watch her face light up when they were in her arms, and the most touching moments is when I see them on each side of her as she reads to them.\n\nKaty is the most remarkable and smartest person I have ever met.   The love of my life and partner forever.  I can''t wait to share the love we have for each with our child.  I know it will be the most rewarding thing for the both of us.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'ABOUT KATY', 909, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1313363961, 0),
