(220, '<p><img style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/JeffreyandJodie/Petrone-1.jpg" alt="" width="425" height="300" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:medium;font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;">Our families shaped our beliefs and values.  Our parents taught us that honesty and acceptance are important to being happy with who you are.  They encouraged us to work hard, pursue our passions and learn all that we can.  We had traditions and fun family time regularly.  Our parents also taught us to be accepting and loving and that our Christian based values and good sense of humor would carry us through the tough times.  </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:medium;font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;">Between us we have two sisters, a brother, three newphews and two grandmothers. Our parents have had stable, loving marriages for nearly 40 years.   Our parents are the foundation of who we are and we are so very thankful for their sacrifices and hard work to help provide stability and opportunities in our lives.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:medium;font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;">We are fortunate that all of our immediate family lives within only a few miles from our home.  Spending holidays and frequent family gatherings are a very important part of our lives!</span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Family', 946, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1323785899, 0),
(366, '<p>Please click <a href="http://www.parentfinder.com/profileflipbook/946-JeffandJodie/946-JeffandJodie.html" target="_blank">here</a> to view Jeffrey and Jodie''s profile flip book</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'E-book Profile', 946, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1323343140, 0),
(222, '<p><span style="font-size:small;"> We always knew that we wanted to have a family and we decided to start trying to have a child about a year after we got married.  Tiff had a miscarriage and we found out that there were other infertility issues as well.  Briefly, we considered IVF, but after speaking with several of our friends who were adopted or have adopted children themselves we knew that adoption was the right path for us.  We both love being around children and are looking forward to the next chapter of our life. <img title="Smile" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/plugins/tiny_mce/plugins/emotions/img/smiley-smile.gif" border="0" alt="Smile" /></span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Why We are Choosing Adoption', 732, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1318196441, 0),
