(258, '<p class="MsoNormal">Hi! :-)</p>\n<p>We are Dan and Rob, and have been together for 10 years.<span>  </span>We are thankful that you have chosen to give the gift of life to your child.<span>  </span>This must be one of the hardest decisions you will have to make, and we appreciate the fact that you are looking at us.<span>  </span>Having made the decision to allow someone else to raise your child, it must be daunting to choose someone to raise that child.<span>  </span>We do hope that you will choose us, but know that whoever you do choose will be the right person to raise him or her.<br />We hope that with this letter and the profile book that you will get a good sense of us and we hope that you will consider us to be the right people to raise your child.<br />We have a row home in a nice section of Baltimore that we bought in 2004.<span>  </span>Not far away from our house is a great elementary school, several beautiful parks and playgrounds.<span>  </span>We love the neighborhood and the community that is around us.<span>  </span>We have several friends in the area with children, and as he or she grows, there will be no lack of playmates for them.<br />Dan works for a Pharmaceutical company, keeping their computers running.<span>  </span>Rob works for a Software company that makes software for Architects and Engineers.<span>  </span>Dan’s Dad lives in Maryland, his mother lives with us, and his brother lives about 5 hours away in Ohio.<span>  </span>Rob’s family lives in Florida, and we get down once a year to visit them.<span>  </span>We also have a larger extended “family” of friends in the area that we love to spend time with.<span>  </span>They have all been quite supportive of us in the adoption process, some even trying to set up play dates for their children.<br />Besides Dan’s mom, we share the house with two cats and a dog.<span>  </span>All of them have been great with the children of our friends, especially our dog.</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Get to know us', 1093, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1346949875, 0),
