(266, 'I was born and raised on the south shore of Long Island NY to a large and loving family.  I have 3 brothers and 1 sister, who all live on the east coast and we see each other quite often.  My Mother was adopted, so I have some understanding of how it makes no difference if your child is your biological offspring or not, as my Grand Parents loved her as their own, perhaps even more so as my mother was a gift fulfilled to them.  I have many hobbies and interests, many of which can be shared with a growing child and for as much of me that is the responsible adult, I am but a kid at heart.  I attended College and graduated with an associate’s degree in Illustration and work as a professional tattoo artist and business owner with two well established and successful business locations.  I also do freelance illustration work on the side.  My career has afforded us to be able to travel all over the world, working as a guest artist in many countries.  We love to travel and adventure, and have been all over America, Europe, Costa Rica, Iceland, Japan, and Bali. I love taking in and learning about the many aspects of different cultures.  I would not label myself a religious person, but I can say with confidence and pride that I am a very Spiritual person, and feel deeply that we are all intrinsically connected.   I am all about Karma and this belief drives me to be the best person I can be.   I know that Jennifer will be an amazing mother to your child.  She has such a huge heart and is always full of smiles.  I see it in her interactions with the children in our extended family and with the children of our friends.  Everyone, young and old, immediately takes to her light and positive energy.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Anthony', 1076, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1320864972, 0),
(267, 'Hello, we are Anthony and Jennifer and we want to thank you for taking the time to look over our profile in consideration for the adoption of the child growing within you. It takes a very brave mother with strength and a lot of guts and we commend you. We can only imagine what feelings you may be going through and the circumstances that have led you to the truly compassionate decision to bring this child to term and seek out a loving family who for whatever reason has chosen the path of adoption. Our own reason for choosing the gift and miracle of adoption comes from years of trying to conceive, but to no avail. Over the past few years, Jennifer had two failed pregnancies which led to the total loss of being able to conceive naturally. IVF was deemed too risky, and we came to the realization that we would much rather provide for an adoptive child and know without a doubt that we would love, cherish, guide, and nurture your child no differently than if the child was our own. We can provide so much opportunity and adventure, and believe in allowing a child the freedom to pursue his or her own interests while introducing lots of new activities and experiences. We have so much joy and love for each other and the world, and we hope to share that love unconditionally if you choose us as adoptive parents.   ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Birth Mother Letter', 1076, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1324097012, 0),
(268, 'I consider myself lucky enough to have grown up in Orlando where I was able to go to Disney as much as I wanted, thanks to my parents who both worked there.  I am the youngest of three (all girls) and was raised by very caring, affectionate and fun parents who worked opposite shifts so they could always be with us.  Anthony and I intend to raise our child in the same manner, always having one of us there with our child and fortunately, my loving and energetic mother lives with us, who is equally ecstatic that we’re going to be blessed with a child.  She can’t wait to shower the baby with love, as does the rest of our family.  Also in our home, we have two wonderful cats and our princess dog who is great with children.  My friends'' kids give her such a hard time but she deals with it impeccably.  I love spending time with my dear friends and am an “Aunt” to those with kids. I also like running, doing arts and crafts, reading, and traveling with my husband.  I am so thankful I caught a man like Anthony, he brings so much pleasure and amusement into my life and into the life of anyone he meets, he is hilarious and always has a great story to tell. Children have so much fun with him; he interacts with them wonderfully.  I can’t wait for him and I to be parents, I know this is where we will really shine.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Jennifer', 1076, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1320865522, 0),
(269, 'In my free time I enjoy reading, drawing, playing with our dog Phoenix, and playing various types of games.  I like to hike and boulder, camping in the woods, parks, and deserts around the country.  Growing up on the water, I love to swim and go to the beach and living where we do we have many beaches in proximity and also many lakes and natural springs.  Not only am I an accomplished artist, but I am also a pretty good cook and love to come up with new and fantastic recipes.\n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Hobbies of Anthony', 1076, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1319084617, 0),
