(313, 'Things I love: sports, photography, cooking, sarcasm, movies, art, food trucks, traveling, our dog Danica, and reading.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Joey', 1247, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1320868907, 0),
(314, '<b>From Joey:</b> To put it simply, Katie is my best friend. We’ve been through many situations in our relationship, and the one constant is that she’s always there for me. She’s there when I need support and guidance or just a good laugh. Katie has an awesome sense of humor and can make me smile easily. We can be happy having a nice dinner at a nice restaurant on vacation, or keeping it low key and eating wings on a Saturday night watching football. Katie has a strong work ethic and has deep conviction in her beliefs, and I know that any child we are fortunate enough to bring home will have the best mother anyone can ask for. Katie will be patient, compassionate, and loving. These are all traits I’ve seen numerous times in the last 9 years. My heart still skips a beat when she smiles at me in the morning, and I know I’m blessed to have another day with her.\n\n<p><b>Things I love (from Katie):</b> writing, photography, traveling, being with family and friends, dogs, listening to music, baking, watching sports, Mexican food, decorating, thunderstorms, going to the beach, and reading.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Katie', 1247, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1327670975, 0);
