(332, 'Lauren is three years old and pretty much runs the household.  We have decided that it is time we try to adopt a sibling because she is getting the "Only Child Syndrome".  She is very loving and loves playing with other kids as well as her black lab Maggie.  She has a great imagination and an amazing sense of humor.  The words, "Time Out", has been added to her vocabulary since she has turned two.  Even on her worst tantrum days, she still brings such joy and happiness to our family.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Lauren Cadence', 1264, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1347929387, 0),
