(337, 'For some reason, our relationship just works.  We are more different then we are alike but for us that is a good thing.  Matt is very laid back, quiet and just goes with the flow of things.  Karrie, on the other hand, is the organizer, energizer and makes sure things get done.  We both clean house, do yard work and cook.  We believe that our relationship is what it is because of our different personalities and the sense of humor that we bring to every situation.  ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Relationship', 1264, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1321482514, 0),
