(339, 'These days, the "non-traditional" family is part of our  everyday culture. We believe that love comes in many shapes and sizes and that having two loving parents is what matters.\n\nThere are many resources for us. But most important is being open, having conversations and raising our kids with love.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'How Two Mommies works', 834, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1357603247, 0),
