(341, 'We met nine years ago by pure happenstance. While doing research for work, Bryan came across Erica’s website. After corresponding for a couple of weeks, we went on our first date. Two years later, we were married. We''re both very creative people who are also passionate about books and food. We love growing some of our own food in our large backyard garden. Bryan does most of the cooking, and we take pleasure in eating dinner together and catching up after work at our dining room table. We enjoy ethnic food - our favorites include Indian, Thai, Middle Eastern, Mexican and Vietnamese. After receiving our master''s degrees in Library Science in Illinois, we moved to Kansas in 2009 where we are both librarians. Bryan is a library manager and Erica is a children''s librarian.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Us', 1272, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1321971259, 0),
