(355, 'On February of 2008 we received our lovely daughter Rebecca. She just brought us closer and our lives had more meaning. Pretty early on our believe that we did not want a only child pushed us to start a international process of adoption responding to family friends assistance. We applied to adopt from Madagascar It took us on a long emotional ride until we arrived home with a all boy 17 month old Josiah that has us laughing and wondering what is next all the time.\nTo see them get along so well and play like they have been together since he was born. Has sparked us again to want to add to our full of love, fun and blessed home.', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our children', 1342, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1322599493, 0),
