(394, 'Please click <a href=http://www.parentfinder.com/profileflipbook/1080-jason_karen/1080-jason_karen.html target= _blank>here</a> to view Jason and Karen''s profile flip book', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'E-book Profile', 1080, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1325026296, 1),
(391, '<p>Dear Expectant Family,</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>We''re Chris and Mara, and we are very happy to have this chance to tell you a little bit about ourselves. We know that we can''t possibly understand the difficult decisions you are facing, and you have our heartfelt respect and compassion. We hope that our profile will give you a glimpse into the kind of life we will provide for a child. We have always wanted to become parents, but we are unable to have biological children. We want to adopt because we believe that families are built on love, trust, and a sense of shared values. We have so much love to give, and we are looking forward to fulfilling our dream of becoming parents through adoption.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>If you select us to be your child''s adoptive family, your child will have a life filled with love, laughter, music, fun, culture, diversity, and learning. We have stable, secure, and flexible jobs that allow us to provide for our family while giving us plenty of time to spend together and with family and friends. We value education and learning and will provide your child with excellent educational opportunities, from the first bedtime stories we read to your child, through college graduation, and beyond. We have a safe and comfortable home that is close to parks, schools, and activities. We love to sing and make music. We have a small, close-knit family and a large, diverse extended family of loving friends, who will all joyfully welcome your child into their lives. We can''t wait to share holidays, family trips and everyday special moments with a child!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Thank you again for taking the time to get to know us better. We hope we can help each other, as you make the best possible decision for your child''s future, and we try to build our forever family.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>With warm wishes,<br />Chris and Mara</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Letter to Expectant Families', 1704, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1332359514, 0),
(395, 'Please click <a href=http://www.parentfinder.com/profileflipbook/1093-danandrobbooks/1093-danandrobbooks.html target= _blank>here</a> to view Daniel and Robert''s profile flip book', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'E-book Profile', 1093, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1325028181, 1),
