(416, '<p>I waited a long time for Mara to come into my life, and I was glad when she finally did because she was so worth waiting for!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Mara knows how to enjoy herself and really laugh.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We''re both musicians, but Mara is such a wonderful singer with a beautiful voice, and musicianship that makes her always a joy to hear and watch.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>She''s so loving with me and everyone she meets. She is perfectly honest, and isn''t afraid to express her confusion in order to further the conversation and bring understanding to everyone. In fact, though I''ve always treated others with great respect and kindness, from watching how Mara treats others, I learned even more about the kind of respect we all deserve and how to give it more openly.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>I love her so much and can''t wait to know the wonderful, empowered person a child who has her as a mother grows up to be.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'What Chris says about Mara', 1704, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1325285202, 0),
(417, '<p>I am so grateful that Chris is my husband. He is warm, patient, affectionate, sensitive, funny and smart. His loving nature, his patience and his sense of fun are going to make him a great dad.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Chris handles even the most stressful situations with patience and humor. Last year, I got sick while we were on vacation and had to take a trip to the emergency room. Chris treated the hospital visit like it was just another stop on our vacation itinerary. He stayed by my side the whole time, chatting with me and making me laugh. Because Chris took the whole thing in stride, we were able to resume our vacation as soon as I felt better with no stress, and we had a wonderful time.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Chris is the most patient and loving person I know. He really knows how to make his friends and family feel special and loved. There is no one else I would rather have by my side during life''s ups and downs. In the best of times, and in the worst of times, Chris is a steady, calm and loving presence. The child who has Chris as a father will be very lucky!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'What Mara says about Chris', 1704, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1325285151, 0),
