(423, 'Work part-time at a movie theatre so I get to see lots of movies!  (also volunteer to be the giant ticket stub mascot)\nLove chocolate...no such thing as a dessert that is too sweet.  Favorite candy bar...Reeses PB cup.\nFavorite food...Hawaiian Pizza.  Favorite drink....tie between root beer and chocolate milk.\nBorn at 12 midnight so my parents got to choose my birthday!  Guilty pleasure...getting a massage and spending the day in my pj''s!  Besides teaching, my other dream jobs would be to be a back-up singer/dancer or create my own greeting cards complete with funny sayings and pictures!  Favorite color...pink.  Favorite flower...tulip.\nFavorite animal...giraffe.  Was the only adult who signed up for tap dance lessons at the YMCA a few years ago.  \nThrew lots of strikes as the pitcher on my childhood softball team...huge fan of Paul Molitor.\n    ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'FUN FACTS ABOUT LISA', 1445, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1325815106, 0),
(424, 'Favorite color: yellow.\n\nFavorite food:  lasagna\n\nFavorite drink: diet Mt DEW\n \nLove being a nurse!\n\nPlayed the trumpet in the high school band and marched in the Mickey Mouse Parade at DISNEY WORLD!\n\nOwn 3 bowling balls and am not even on a bowling league.\n\nOk, when I was younger I was a very successful bowler winning many trophies!\n\nSwam with dolphins at Sea World.\n\nWent down hill Skiing at Lake Taho with a professional Hot Dog Skier.\n\nEnjoy mountain biking. \n\nCertified CPR instructor.\n\n\n\n    \n ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Fun facts about Jeremy', 1445, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1326424391, 0),
