(425, 'Our home lies in a quiet neighborhood filled with families and small children. We have a three bedroom house with plenty of room to explore and play. Bordering our home is a playground, a walking trail, the metro park system, and the local recreation center.\nWe have lived in our home for eight years and find it to be warm and welcoming. Our house is within five miles of Bill''s parents and his sister and her family. ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Home', 1765, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1327888238, 0),
(426, 'In Bill''s Words...\nHolly is the most caring person I know. She does an excellent job taking care of me. She is a great cook and the prettiest girl I know. Her biggest asset is her unselfish devotion to those around her. Holly is a great teacher, my best friend and I am lucky to have her as my wife. I know she will make a terrific mom. ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Holly', 1765, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1325985647, 0),
(427, 'In Holly''s Words...\nBill is the love of my life. He''s a husband and best friend all in one. I love him more than words can express.\nHis most outstanding characteristics are his loyalty to family and friends, hard work and dedication to each project he takes on, and his sense of adventure. \n\nBill will be a wonderful father. He is so full of energy and always ready to discover something new. ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Bill', 1765, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1329096281, 0),
(435, 'Together, we love to run, hike, see old movies, go to amusement parks, and attend football, baseball, and hockey games. Our favorite pasttime and passion is roller skating, which is how we met 17 years ago.\n\nOne of our favorite hobbies is traveling. We love to take time away and discover new and exciting places. We  travel two to three times per year. In early February, we plan a weekend getaway to a quiet bed and breakfast. We love to take the time to relax and enjoy each other. Each spring, we take a week to visit Holly''s mom in Florida. We love spending time with family and usually try to make a stop at Disney. During the summer months we take a week away, sometimes staying close to home or traveling abroad.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Bill and Holly As a Couple...', 1765, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1329095252, 0),
