(449, 'As adopting parents we cannot imagine the thoughts and feelings you''re having at this time. As you plan the future of your baby, please know if you choose us as parents for your child we will respect your wishes of openness. We understand the need to watch this baby grow and develop and are accepting of open, semi-open, or closed adoptions.\nWe would love to keep you up to date with exciting events that are happening in his or her life with an openness mutually agreed upon. It would be a blessing to share the wonderful gift you have given us.\n ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Openness', 1765, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1329692824, 0),
