(537, 'Written by Syd:\n\nRoy is my best friend.  He is the most beautiful man I have ever met.  He is kind, loving, and honest, Roy is my whole world.  I knew early on in our dating relationship that my then, boyfriend, would make a wonderful husband and an incredible father.\n  The way I view it is that if we were to have the pleasure of raising a little girl, I would love to see her find a life partner like Roy; after eight years of marriage, he still opens the car door for me and puts on and takes off my coat, truly a gentleman.  Our entire dating relationship was more like a fairy tale.  The respect my prince charming has constantly shown to me had borne fruit with a purity in our dating relationship.  If we were to have the privilege of raising a little boy, he would have a great role model, especially in learning how to treat women.  Truly, children are most influenced by what they see.\nRoy''s greatest attribute is his love for God.  Because he cares so deeply not to offend God''s heart, I have found it easy to trust him with my own.\nRoy''s charm has overflowed into his interactions with children over the nine years we''ve been together.  From working with a Children''s Ministry, teaching faith formation to Seventh Graders, spending quality time with our god-children, and playing with our many friend''s kids, Roy has a wonderful way of connecting with and bringing a smile to a child''s face.  How common it is that after he''s had just a small amount of time to get to know one of these little ones, that child is running after Roy wanting more of his loving attention.\nRoy is my window to everything that is beautiful.  \n\n\n\n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'ABOUT ROY', 2067, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1330566621, 0),
(538, '<p><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">Jon was born and raised in Rhinelander, Wisconsin. His parents are William and Dawn who also live in Rhinelander. He has one older sister Jenny who has been married to her husband Wayne for over 12 years. They have two children Alyssa who is 5 and Trenton who is 2. They also live in Rhinelander.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">Carrie was born and raised in Merrill, Wisconsin, except for the 3 years when she was little when the family lived in Alaska. Her parents are Garth and Freida who still reside in Merrill. She has one older sister who lives in New York, New York and a younger brother who lives in Merrill, Wisconsin.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">We love getting together and spending time with our families for dinners, movies, playing games and sitting around talking and laughing together. Our  families are excited about adding a new member to the family and are ready to welcome you and your child with open arms.</span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'OUR FAMILY', 1573, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1330556552, 0),
