(575, 'We met in the fall of 2006.  Recognizing that ours was a special relationship, we were introduced to each other’s parents within weeks of our first date.  We believe that God brought us together when he did for a reason.  Sadly Jerry’s father passed away a month after we started dating.  We are grateful that Kiley was able to meet him. \n\nWe each feel that we are blessed to have the other in our lives and we thank God for that.  We are each other’s best friend and we cherish the time we spend together.  We often enjoy walks around the lake near our house, running, biking, playing with our pets, and sitting together for morning coffee before we start our day.   We always manage to have a good time and to make each other laugh no matter where we are or what we are doing.\n\n\n\nWe belong to a terrific Christian church which has an extraordinary children''s program and we look forward to introducing our little one to everyone there. We firmly believe that God intended for us to grow our family through adoption and we feel so fortunate to have this opportunity to begin our family.  \n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About us', 1679, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1331387487, 0),
(576, '<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">We met in the fall of 2006.  Recognizing that ours was a special relationship, we were introduced to each other’s parents within weeks of our first date.  We believe that God brought us together when he did for a reason.  Sadly Jerry’s father passed away a month after we started dating.  We are grateful that Kiley was able to meet him.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">We each feel that we are blessed to have the other in our lives and we thank God for that.  We are each other’s best friend and we cherish the time we spend together.  We often enjoy walks around the neighborhood, running, biking, playing with our pets, and sitting together for morning coffee before we start our day.   We always manage to have a good time and to make each other laugh no matter where we are or what we are doing.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">We have done some traveling as a couple and we enjoy exploring new places and destinations together.  We are excited to experience these adventures as a family!  We also love to spend time with our friends, whom we consider part of our extended family.  We meet quite often for: children’s birthday parties, barbeques, Halloween and Christmas parties, sporting events, or to just get together.   We treasure these times and look forward to introducing our child into the group of children that are becoming fast friends due to their parents being such longtime friends.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;"><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">After living in New England and Massachusetts for many years, we have had a wonderful opportunity to move to Florida. We are very excited to be close to Kiley’s family.</span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About us', 1679, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1350136102, 0),
(577, '<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">Our parents get along very well and like to spend time together. Our mothers like to chat over a cup of tea when they visit. We are blessed to have such an amazing and supportive family. It is wonderful for us that our families get along so well.  Our parents and siblings are thrilled that we have chosen adoption and are looking forward to spoiling their next grandchild, niece or nephew.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;"> </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">Your child will be able to play with cousins close to his or her own age. We are very close with Kiley’s brother and his wife.  Kiley’s brother has four young children. Having them close by in Florida is a lot of fun. We speak to them almost daily and visit them numerous times throughout the year. We all like being able to spend time with them as a family. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;"> </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">Jerry’s family is in Massachusetts. We visit during summer vacations and our niece Kayla likes to visit us in Florida during her school vacations. She loves to help Kiley cook and can’t get enough of the beach.   Jerry’s older brother lives close by and we are able to spend time with him and his longtime girlfriend at all the major holidays. Jerry’s twin brother recently got married! His wife brought two girls to the family. We are looking forward to getting to know our two new nieces as well as spending time with his brother’s daughter who we have a close relationship with.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;"> </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:medium;">We also enjoy attending our annual family reunions.  Everyone in our extended family is loving and supportive and they are all excited to welcome the newest member.</span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Family', 1679, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1350068280, 0),
