(597, 'We met 14 years ago and after dating for only 6 months we knew that we were right for each other.  A year later we were married.  Our marriage is one of trust, love, understanding, respect, and honor. We both appreciate what we have in our relationship and know that we are very lucky to have found each other.  We are easy going and have a relationship filled with open communication.  In our free time together we enjoy golfing, being outdoors on our 10 acres, and playing with our chocolate lab, Hank.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Chris and Jill', 2428, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1331774335, 0),
