(634, '<p><span style="font-size:medium;color:#993366;"><strong>Thank you for visiting our profile.  </strong></span></p>\n<p>Please visit our adoption website to see even more photos, read our blog, download our adoption profile and much more...</p>\n<p><a title="Ben and Susan Adoption Website - Blog" href="http://www.ben-and-sue-adopt-wi.com/">http://www.ben-and-sue-adopt-wi.com/</a></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Website', 2405, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1333056354, 0),
(636, '<div>\n<div>Are you a birth mother with an adoption plan or looking for some great parents for your new born?\n<p>We hope that you are doing what is right for you. We hope you are considering parenting. But if you know that is not for you we have. We are prepared to be parents now!</p>\n<h2>We hope you look at our parent profile here on parentfinder and that we will be a great match for your baby.</h2>\n<p>We want to make sure you know there are options other than abortion. Whether you choose to parent or choose adoption we support your decision.</p>\n</div>\n</div>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Birth Mother seeking family - We are ready to adopt', 1787, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1334098965, 0),
