(638, '3 years old\n\n\nNever meets a stranger\n\n\nLoves to sings\n\n\nLoves to "play" the piano, guitar, harmonica, flute, drum, & violin\n\n\nLoves to play with his cars, trucks, & tractors\n\n\n\nLandon was adopted & knows this is how we became a family.  We talk to him about it often & talk about his birthparents.  It''s a very positive thing for him.\nWe told him one day we would have another baby, he said "Right now God has the baby".  He is such a sweetie!', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'ABOUT LANDON', 2580, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1333162424, 0),
