(645, '<p><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;"> <span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;">We have lived in the  same house for almost 9 years.  <span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;"><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;">Our house is <strong>spacious, warm, &amp; cozy</strong>.  We have a <strong>large finished basement. </strong>Our<strong> large fenced-in yard </strong>backs up to an<strong> awesome creek</strong> that we can see out our windows.  We love eating outside on our deck &amp; enjoying the <strong>sights &amp; sounds of nature</strong>.  We also take <strong>walks along the creek</strong> with Landon &amp; pretend like we are on a great adventure.</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;"><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;">We love our neighborhood.  We live in a low traffic cul-de-sac <strong>with  multiple parks</strong> and a <strong>year-round swimming pool</strong> within walking distance.  We have <strong>excellent neighbors</strong> who are some of  our closest friends, and there are several young children near-by. </span></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;"><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;"> </span></span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'HOME SWEET HOME', 2580, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1334197772, 0),
