(649, 'Jake is 3 years old and is showing interest in:\n\nMusic. Drums. Guitars. Cars. Disney. Dinosaurs. Dirt. Basketball. Baseball. More Dirt. Playing with Zoe dog. Hanging out with both sets of Grandparents. Playing with his friends. Reading. Ice Cream. Playgrounds. Dirt. Trains. Swimming. Hikes. Ocean. Laughing. Snuggles. Elmo!!', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Interests of Jake', 2552, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1333488150, 0),
