(652, 'While our adoption journey is filled with excitement and anticipation, we realize that you must be experiencing a host of other emotions focusing on what will be the best decision for your baby.  We admire your courage and appreciate the strength that you have in taking the steps necessary to provide your baby with a loving and caring home.  We can''t imagine how difficult your decision will be and hope that you find comfort knowing that your baby will be raised by a loving family who will make sure he/she knows just how special you are.  We would also welcome the opportunity for you to get to know us better through emails, letters or meeting.  Afterwards, we would also be open to sharing updates and pictures as your baby grows if you would like.  \n\nA child in our family will experience the love and affection of an extended family of grandparents, great grandparents, aunts, uncles, great aunts, great uncles and cousins.  Our family is full of excitement at our decision to add to our family through adoption and can''t wait for our new family member to arrive.  We are also fortunate to have friends who are as close to us as family, who are also thrilled for a new addition. \n\nContact us through our agency Forever Families Through Adoption toll-free at 1-866-922-3678 or email us at fromfivetosix@gmail.com', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Thoughts on Adoption', 2532, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1333912016, 0),
(653, '<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color:#000080;font-size:small;">While our adoption journey is filled with excitement and anticipation, we realize that you must be experiencing a host of other emotions focusing on what will be the best decision for your baby.  We admire your courage and appreciate the strength that you have in taking the steps necessary to provide your baby with a loving and caring home.  We can''t imagine how difficult your decision will be and hope that you find comfort knowing that your baby will be raised by a loving family who will make sure he/she knows just how special you are.  We would also welcome the opportunity for you to get to know us better through emails, letters or meeting.  Afterwards, we would also be open to sharing updates and pictures as your baby grows if you would like.  </span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color:#000080;font-size:small;">A child in our family will experience the love and affection of an extended family of grandparents, great grandparents, aunts, uncles, great aunts, great uncles and cousins.  Our family is full of excitement at our decision to add to our family through adoption and can''t wait for our new family member to arrive.  We are also fortunate to have friends who are as close to us as family, who are also thrilled for a new addition. </span></p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> </span></p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color:#000080;font-size:small;">Visit our website at www.parentprofile.net</span></p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000080;font-size:small;">call us toll-free at 1-888-91adopt </span><span style="color:#000080;font-size:small;">or </span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color:#000080;font-size:small;">email us at <a href="mailto:fromfivetosix@gmail.com">fromfivetosix@gmail.com</a></span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Some Thoughts on Adoption', 2532, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1357107971, 0),
(654, 'http://www.parentprofile.net \nPlease visit us and send us an email to let us know you were there!  fromfivetosix@gmail.com\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our website', 2532, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1339547336, 0);
