(665, 'Playing with the kids, restoring antique tractors, trucks and cars, vacations, reading, Rock Band, reading, teaching, swimming, truck shows.\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Interests of Kirk', 2683, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1334075571, 0),
(666, 'We love open adoption.  We will honor YOU as a child''s birth parent or family member and will keep an open adoption with you.  We are NOT going to close the door on you like so many adoptive parents do....\n\nWe are fun, honest and truly love our children and one another.   We aren''t perfect people.  We are real, normal and fun parents.   I''m proud that I still rock out to Soundgarden and refuse to drive a minivan.  Ha :)   Kirk isn''t your typical dad, either.  He loves to pull practical jokes on the kids and isn''t your uptight kind of dad who won''t have fun.  He''s the opposite.  As a teacher, he NEEDS to laugh in order to stay sane!\n\nOur kids are awesome and amazing.  They are brilliant, too.  I''m a tad biased.  But seriously, they have overcome so many obstacles (Autism to Developemental Delays) and shown that time, therapies and TONS of love can bring you to the stars.   We never quit.   Ever.\n\n<b>You are not giving your child up.  Instead?  You are giving your child more.  More opportunities....dance lessons, sports, stability, college.....tons of love and an ongoing relationship with YOU!</b>\n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Why Choose Us?', 2683, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1334078195, 0),
