(670, 'We live in a 100 restored farmhouse on about 10 acres of land.  We have our own woods and noisy creek at the back of the property.  Our house is only about a mile from the local elementary, middle and high schools but it feels like we are really in the country.   I love having roosters wake us up in the morning and watching the deer come graze at dusk.  \n\nWe have 5 bedrooms and there is a HUGE one complete with a fireplace (non-working) and its'' own bathroom and custom closet ready and waiting.  \n\nWe also have a playground, pool, and tons of space to run and have FUN.   \n\n\n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Home', 2683, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1334090306, 0),
(671, 'From Kirk: Hello and Greetings! I am here to tell you a bit about Jules.\n \nFirst off, she is the best wife and mother I could ever ask for! She loves us all like no one else could. She is beautiful both inside and out and I am so thankful to have her in our lives. Our children are gentle souls who love to help out and care for others. I think they have learned so much of that from Jules. She is constantly doing something for her friends or even for people she hardly knows. She just cares so much about others. She truly is an inspiration to me and to our children. She would be a wonderful mother to your child.\n \nI can promise you that your child will always be comforted with hugs and love whenever she has a boo-boo, she will always be praised for doing her best work when coloring a picture, and she will have a mommy and daddy who love her unconditionally. \n\n\n<a href="http://s1191.photobucket.com/albums/z475/juliea388/Facebook/Instagram%20Photos/?action=view&amp;current=549113_10150788469823343_632428342_11861991_403312462_n.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://i1191.photobucket.com/albums/z475/juliea388/Facebook/Instagram%20Photos/549113_10150788469823343_632428342_11861991_403312462_n.jpg" border="0" alt="http://instagr.am/p/JICs7bEieg/"></a>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'ABOUT JULIE', 2683, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1334090387, 0),
