(688, '<p>Our daughter is the love of our life and full of spunk. A total Diva we like to call her. She is full of energy and loves exploring new things.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Her likes:</strong> Bubbles, horses, dogs, Princesses, Mermaids, Story Time, Painting, Pasta (any kind), chocolate</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Her Dislikes</strong>: Really Loud noises, automatic toilets (gross but true ;), spiders, bees, onions</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>School Grade:</strong> Preschool</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Age:</strong> 4</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><img style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/bkadoption/_DSC02525.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="199" />Our little cheeseball!</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About our Daughter', 2654, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1334182162, 0),
(689, '<p><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/bkadoption/2010_CA_Trip_06217.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></p>\n<p>Waiting in line at Disneyland</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/bkadoption/F12E311E4.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="192" /></p>\n<p>Brandon with our old dogs RIP</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/bkadoption/A8A016253.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="435" /></p>\n<p>Kim Fly Fishing with Friends</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/bkadoption/F6160FB9.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="203" /></p>\n<p>Brandon with our daughter at 3 months old</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/bkadoption/7.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></p>\n<p>Family photo 2008</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/bkadoption/January_2011_01812.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></p>\n<p>Our daughter''s Third Birthday</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Crazy Life!', 2654, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1334182515, 0),
(690, '<p><strong>Brandon</strong> has 3 brothers and 3 sisters in his family. We have 6 nieces and 2 (almost 3) nephews on his side of the family. He grew up in Southern California where his dad worked for the LAPD SWAT team. The majority of his family now lives within 20 minutes of us. He also has a sister still in CA and another sister in CO.</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/bkadoption/IMG_7623small_1.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/bkadoption/waldron_family_pics_001.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="167" /></p>\n<p><strong>Kim </strong>has 2 brothers and 1 sister. She grew up mostly in Eastern Washington. Her father was in the Navy and when she was young they moved around frequently when he was reassigned. Her parents now live in TX. Both of her brothers live within 15 minutes of us and her sister lives in OR. We have 1 niece and 3 nephews on her side of the family.</p>\n<p><img style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/bkadoption/DSCN0862.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="337" /></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Families', 2654, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1334183031, 0),
(691, 'Our situation for childcare couldn''t be more ideal! Our work schedules allow for Michael (who shares a small family business) to be home most of the day with our child, as he works late afternoon to early evening...with lots of flexibility.  Beth (an elementary school teacher), obviously has the perfect "working parent" schedule...off for holidays and summers! Both of our occupations allow for us to be accessible and "hands on" with our child.  Additionally both sets of our parents live within 10 miles of us...and all 4 of them are eager to put in some "grandparent time" with a little one.  As a strong family unit...we can assure you that our child will be cared for and attended to, without any difficulties.  We are also blessed with SEVERAL friends and family members who have little ones...all awaiting some fun and special "play dates" once we are placed with a baby!  We are blessed with such a fun and fabulous support system! ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Childcare Plan', 2395, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1335182049, 0),
