(693, '<strong>Are you a birth mother with an adoption plan or <h3>looking for some adoptive parents</h3> for you new born?</strong><br>\n<p>We want you to have all the resources you need to make the decision that is right for you and your baby. Whether that is parenting or <h3>looking for a family to adopt baby </h3> <br><p>We have <h4><a href="http://familyhopingtoadopt.blogspot.com/p/birthmother-resources.html"> Expectant Mother resources </a> </h4>available on our blog.</p><br>\n<p><strong><h2>We hope you look at our parent profile here on parentfinder and that we will be a great match for you and your baby.</h2></p></strong><br>\n<p>We want to make sure you know there are options other than abortion. Wether you choose to parent or choose adoption we support your decsion. </p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'BIRTH MOTHER SEEKING FAMILY - WE ARE READY TO ADOPT', 2654, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1334340587, 0),
(694, '<p><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">So much fun to capture us and our life and create </span><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">hardback books...</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;"><img style="float:right;" title="Jake''s story books" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/LauraRyan/DSC04314.JPG" alt="Jake''s story books" width="350" height="263" /></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;">Since Jake''s Open Adoption in 2009, we''ve been making storybooks for him to read and learn. To learn of "his story" ... the story of his Birthparents and Adoption Journey. </span><span style="font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:small;">To learn his ABC''s and 123''s and Zoo Animals. To learning about his Adopted Chosen Family and Holidays. We hope that he treasures these books and enjoys watching himself grow up in each page. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:xx-small;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><br /></span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'The Story of our lives', 2552, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1334512853, 0),
(695, 'We met through a mutual friend who set us up on a blind date.  After a year and a half of dating we were engaged and we have been married for 14 years.    Family is very important to us and both of our families live nearby, so we spend a lot of time doing fun things together.  The holidays are extra special including celebrations with both of our families and extended relatives.  Your child will have four grandparents, nine cousins and eight aunts and uncles.  We especially love spending time with our 5 nieces and 4 nephews.  We love to go to their music and ballet recitals and their sporting events.  We enjoy playing with our 8 year old calico cat Ginger who is very friendly and loves to be around people.  We both like going to the movies, working in the yard together, traveling, swimming at our relatives’ house and going to plays and musicals.  We attend Catholic Church together on a regular basis and we both volunteer at our church as well. We look forward to having children and after dealing with years of infertility, we are excited to build our family through adoption.  ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Family Story', 2576, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1351877715, 0),
(696, 'We are both City Planners for major Cities in New Jersey.  We enjoy our jobs because we enjoy working in the public center and with community.  Besides enjoying work we love enjoying all that life has to offer -friends, family, and having fun.  ', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Us', 2272, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1334498997, 0),
(697, '<p>We have a huge park near our house. This picture shows just a tiny part of it. Huge open fields, bike trails, a creek, a bridge, playground equipment, a tank, picnic shelters, baseball fields, soccer fields and so much more. So much fun! We also have a clubhouse, tennis courts and swimming pool in our neighborhood and we belong to a swimming pool that is enclosed during the winter for year-around swimming. We can ride our bike to the pools and the park. The front of our neighborhood has ponds and fountains ... plenty of geese, ducks and fishing there! Also close by ... the grocery, restaurants, medical care, and the movie theater!</p>\n<p><img style="vertical-align:bottom;" title="Jake and Zoe park walk" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/LauraRyan/JakeZoe_Park_Walk.JPG" alt="Jake and Zoe park walk" width="310" height="232" /></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Neighborhood', 2552, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1334513736, 0),
(698, 'We met at a mutual friend''s birthday party several years ago and got married in 2006. While dating, we found that we had very similar backgrounds. We are both from small towns in Tennessee and attended college right after high school. We both grew up in middle-class, Christian families who provided us with structure, security, and love. Nathan''s parents are retired and live close to us. His brother lives about two hours away, along with two nephews. Ginger''s parents live an hour away. Her mom is a nurse, and her dad works as an insurance broker. Ginger''s brother lives near Nashville with his wife and seven-year-old daughter. Her sister lives about ten minutes away, and they are very close. She also has a grandmother who lives in Indiana and another grandmother in Florida.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Us', 1640, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1334525399, 0),
(699, '<p><span style="font-size:large;font-family:&quot;comic sans ms&quot;, sans-serif;">We both love watching movies, spending time with family and friends, sightseeing, and playing with our dogs. We are members of a local Baptist church where Nathan volunteers as a TV camera director and is involved in a church visitation ministry. We both volunteer in the nursery and are active in our Sunday School class.</span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Interests', 1640, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1334540327, 0),
