(727, 'Greetings:\n\nThank you for taking the time to get to know me. My name is Ericka. I am a single female who is looking to open her heart and her home to a child. It has been a dream of mine for many years to adopt a child and I feel now is a wonderful time to raise a child. I am a Family Practice physician in Virginia who loves children. I spend my days taking care of other people''s children, now I am ready to have a child at my home. I cannot tell you how grateful I am that you have chosen this path of adoption. Without you, my dream would never become a reality. Thank you for your generous gift to myself and humanity. \n\nI, Ericka am a single adult who was raised in a small town. I have a younger brother who lives in California. Here in Virginia, my mother and I have a beautiful home in a suburban area. When I finish work, I love to participate in church activities, read, sew arts and crafts as well as practice martial arts. My most favorite thing to do is to sit on our back deck, listen to music on a warm summer’s day as the wind blows through my hair. \n\nI am strong in my catholic faith. I attend church regularly. While at church, I am active in parish activities and I am a soloist in the church choir. The best thing I can do with my voice is honor God with it. \n\nAll children are a blessing. You should know that your child will have a loving, safe and secure home. Along with myself, there will be lots of family and friends around at all times to make sure of this.  I promise to give all that I have in this world to make sure that your child will always know that he or she is deeply and unconditionally loved in every way.\n\nThank you for taking the time to read about me. May you have a lifetime of good health and happiness!\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Letter to Birthmother', 2396, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1335495040, 0),
