(733, '<p>We live in a spacious, sunny 4 bedroom house with amazing views of the mountains from the backyard.  Our house is a little over a mile from town, which has shops, a farmer''s market, and the university where we work.  Because it''s a college town, there are excellent schools here, and the town itself is extremely diverse.  Our neighborhood is friendly, and filled with kids who play up the block at the playground, ride their bikes and scooters past our house, or come over to play in our yard with Oz.  In the summer, we love to hang out with our neighbors at the pool, too.</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Home', 2173, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1335933987, 0),
