(763, 'Nick and I met through my step-father.  We truly believe that God put us on earth to find each other. Nick''s past made him a very understanding and accepting person.  Once our relationship became serious and we talkied about a future, Nick was completely understanding and supporive of the fact that I would not be able to have children.  I knew then that I wanted to spend the rest of my life with him.\n\nNick and I are best friends. We cry together and laugh together.  Having so much in common, like our love for sports and the outdoors, makes everyday life fun and easy!  Of course, not everyday is easy and fun.  We have our difficulties, as does every couple, but we work through them as a couple.  Our love for each other is strong enough that the rough patches don''t break us.  As much love as we share, there is still a whole in our hearts which we wish to fill with the blessing of a child.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Story- by Shannon', 2871, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1337922982, 0),
