(773, '   Elle is our daughter, who was born in the spring of 2011. She is healthy and happy—and sunshine incarnate. She wakes up smiling and enjoys eating and laughing. Her favorite foods are bananas, asparagus, an hummus. She loves visiting the zoo with Papi (Alan) and singing the golden oldies and dancing around the kitchen with 아빠 (Sam). We both respond when she calls for her “Da-da-da-da!”\n    With Elle, we’ve realized how much we love being fathers and how much we would love to fill the other empty bedroom in our home. \n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'ABOUT ELLE', 2877, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1337128655, 0),
