(794, '<p>We are a happy, loving family who truly enjoy spending time together.  We are so anxious to share our love with a new child.  Being in a large family has so many benefits and having siblings as wonderful, caring and loving as Brianna, Alex and Maya will be a gift to your child.  They cannot wait to shower a new sibling with love and affection as they do each other.</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/fromfivetosix/IMG_7246.jpg" alt="" width="290" height="435" />   <img style="float:right;" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/fromfivetosix/IMG_8118.jpg" alt="adoptive siblings" width="290" height="435" /><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/fromfivetosix/IMG_0897.JPG" alt="" width="300" height="200" />  <img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/fromfivetosix/IMG_5375_2.JPG" alt="" width="290" height="268" /></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Siblings Are Awesome', 2532, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1343952757, 0),
