(804, 'Dear Beautiful Baby...\n     In reality, we have not met, but in our dreams, we have felt you a million times and more.  While noone can predict how or when you will come into our lives, we are certain that the love we have for you has begun growing in our hearts...and the respect and adoration for your birthparent(s) will always be there.  \n     We want to be hands-on parents that encourage you to soar to new heights with each and every success and help you to pick up the pieces from any pitfalls you may encounter in your precious life.\n     God''s plan to place you in our home is unique and special...just like you will be. \n      More than anything...we want you to always know you are loved.  We will find ways each and every day to tell you we love you.  Through smiles and giggles, messes and meals, full-on energy and quiet rest, we will treasure the memories we make with you. \n      We will be your parents...you will be our child.\n      We will be your quiet place...you will be our wild.\n      We will be your calm face...you will be our giggle.\n      We will be your wait...you will be our wiggle.\n      We will be your carriage ride...you will be our queen or king.\n      We will be your push...you will be our swing.\n      We will be your audience...you will be our clown.\n      We will be your London Bridges...you will be our falling down.\n      We will be your carrot sticks...you will be our licorice.\n      We will be your dandelion...you will be our first wish.\n      We will be your water wings...you will be our deep.\n      We will be your open arms...you will be our running leap.\n      We will be your way home...you will be our new path.\n      We will be your dry towel...you will be our wet bath.\n      We will be your dinner...you will be our chocolate cake.\n      We will be your bedtime...you will be our wide-awake.\n      We will be your finish line...you will be our race.\n      We will be your praying hands...you will be our saying grace.\n      We will be your favorite book...you will be our new lines.\n      We will be your night light...you will be our starshine.\n      We will be your lullaby...you will be our peek-a-boo.\n      We will be your goodnight kiss...you will be our I love you! \n\nWe can''t wait to meet you!\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'To Our Future Child...', 2395, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1339722835, 0),
