(806, '<p><strong><em><span> </span></em></strong><span style="font-family:&quot;book antiqua&quot;, palatino;font-size:small;">We live in the great state of Minnesota, and love the outdoors. We have a small hobby farm and raise miniature cattle, one sheep, and a small coop of chickens. We love to do many outdoor activities as a family. You will find us biking many of Minnesotas great trails, fishing (our farm is inbetween 3 lakes!), going for a hike or walking, kayaking, or spending the day at the beach. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:&quot;book antiqua&quot;, palatino;font-size:small;">Our home is new, and has plenty of space for a new member! <img title="Smile" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/plugins/tiny_mce/plugins/emotions/img/smiley-smile.gif" border="0" alt="Smile" /> We have a large backyard with a swing set and fort, and lots of room to bike, run, and a play tag. We often spend summer evenings with family and friends, in our backyard around a bonfire. We also love to make us of all the fun a farm has to offer. We take fall hayrides, have our family over to bob for apples and even do gunny sack races!  </span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Home / Life Style', 2964, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1339704864, 0),
(807, '<p>Andrew is an energetic 7 year old. Who is patiently waiting to be a big brother.</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Andrew', 2964, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1339704916, 0),
(808, '<p><span><em><strong>About Andrew -</strong></em></span><br />Andrew is an energetic seven year old, with a hilarious sense of humor. He loves legos, toy tractors, biking, and playing pretend.  He’s a happy go lucky little boy, who –literally- skips everywhere he goes!  He is very ready for a sibling, and has been wishing for one for over three years.  He’s even asked us for bunk beds, because he wants to share his room! We should mention, he also loves to snorkel in the bathtub <img title="Smile" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/plugins/tiny_mce/plugins/emotions/img/smiley-smile.gif" border="0" alt="Smile" /><img style="float:left;" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/lisaandaaron/IMG_1312.JPG" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Andrew', 2964, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1339705448, 0),
