(831, 'I''m most interested in being the best husband and father I can be to my family. I work hard to provide for them so that I can enjoy quality time with them when I''m not working. I enjoy having fun with Heidi and the kids at Disney World, mini-golfing, eating out, playing video games or whatever we decide to do together. I plan a few date nights per month with Heidi and take her on 2 or 3 mini-vacations per year without the kids. I love playing basketball and baseball with our kids, reading with them and just spending time playing with them. I also enjoy our church and the activities that our kids participate in there, vacationing, golf, basketball, going to the movies and watching NASCAR.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Interests and Hobbies of Steve', 3160, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1341082863, 0),
(832, 'I absolutely love teaching our children and being able to enjoy every moment of their lives as we grow together as a family. I thrive on listening to people share their testimonies of what God is doing in their lives. I anticipate our numerous family vacations and trips to Walt Disney World and am blessed to be constantly surprised by short vacation getaways with Steve. I cherish time spent with our extended family and the many friends we have made through our church, homeschool group, sports, our scouting organization. community service and other organized activities. I enjoy reading. I like to plan parties and special events.  I love watching our children play sports and use their God-given talents for the enjoyment of others in piano, scouts, sports and through church plays and activities. As a family we enjoy volunteering regularly at church and in our community. I love to cook. I take many pictures and have a private blog that I try to update weekly for our children to have a written record of their lives. I enjoy a wide range of music and movies. I love Jesus, family, friends and fun! My hobbies include: Teaching, training and having never-ending fun with our children, date nights with my husband, time with my girlfriends, serving/volunteering in our church and community, blogging, vacationing, reading, cooking and any time spent with friends and family.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Interests and Hobbies of Heidi', 3160, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1352470364, 0),
