(1195, 'After we remodeled our condo, we decided to scale up our domestic projects. So we bought a house. 3 bedrooms, 2 Baths, open floor plan, with a playroom perfect basement, looking onto a fenced in backyard, and plenty of room to keep building. Filled with the thunder of kitty paws, the smell of Amanda''s baking, and Brad''s building...It is missing a baby''s laughing. (Oh, ya, and Norman, the squirrel, lives in the tree out back. The kitties REALLY like Norman.)', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Home', 3769, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1356994308, 0),
