(1403, '  We are happy to hear that there will be another child entering this world! We pray that you choose us to parent him or her. This child would learn a lot about large and small families, working hard, enjoying life, and how to be religious in his/her own way.\n  We will together teach basic life lessons. Jenna could share knowledge of how to care for self and the home. Brian would teach about the farm, care for animals and plants.\n  We want to thank you for looking at our profile and pray this child gets the life they deserve. We know your decision will be best and if you chose us we will make sure this child knows how loved they are.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Dear Birth Parent', 5115, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1372317813, 0),
