(1446, 'I''m an expecting mother of a baby boy. I''m a recent college graduate, currently living with my parents in my childhood home. I was adopted as an infant, and because of my experience with adoption, I''m only considering open adoption for my child. I''m a musician with a degree in education and a minor in English. Education and the ability to explore interests is very important to me when considering the future of my child. Although I consider my pregnancy a blessing, I am not in a place in my life where I am able to provide for, care for, and love my child as much as I would like, however I would like to be part of his life in some capacity. ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Me', 6037, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1375628321, 0),
