(847, '\n\n\nWe have been together for over 9 years. We met on February 14th, 2003 - Of all places, in a movie theater with a group of close friends.\n\n We had an instant connection; talking and laughing throughout the movie and dinner following. It didn''t take long to see how strong our bond is.\n\n As our lives grew together we knew being together and growing a family together is our goal.\n\n\nOver seven years ago on May 15th, 2005 we committed our lives together and married. We had a  very romantic destination wedding in Vermont. Our parents and family attended our wedding.\n\n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'HOW WE MET', 3235, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1343077170, 0),
(920, '<p><strong><span style="font-size:small;font-family:verdana, geneva;">Michael comes from a very close and diverse family. He is one of 4 siblings. </span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size:small;font-family:verdana, geneva;">He has two older sisters and a younger brother. His relationship with his parents and all of his siblings is very close and considers them to be much more than siblings, they are all also very close friends.</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size:small;font-family:verdana, geneva;"> </span></strong><br /><strong><span style="font-size:small;font-family:verdana, geneva;">Each of his 3 siblings all have children totaling 11 nephews and nieces. His oldest sister has 4 children, her oldest daughter has 4 children (the oldest named after Michael), her second oldest has 1, and her two youngest not yet. His second oldest sister has 4 boys, the youngest is adopted and also named after Michael; and Michael''s youngest brother has 3 small children. All are hoping that Michael and Khang add a child to their family.</span></strong></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Michael&#039;s Family', 3235, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1363876960, 0),
(921, '<p><span style="font-family:verdana, geneva;font-size:small;"><strong>Khang comes from a large and loving family.</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana, geneva;font-size:small;"><strong>He is one of 5 siblings. He has two older sisters, an older brother and a younger brother. When Khang''s mother passed away 18 years ago Khang took on the role of head of the family and taking care of his ill father.</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana, geneva;font-size:small;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana, geneva;font-size:small;"><strong>His siblings look to him and Michael for help and guidance. Both of Khang''s sisters have children. His oldest sister has one child, and his second oldest just gave birth to her second child a few months ago. Khang''s siblings are looking forward to Khang and Michael''s adoption of a baby with open arms.</strong></span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Khang&#039;s Family', 3235, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1363877000, 0),
(848, 'We have always known we wanted lots of children! Crystal was told as a teenager that she couldn''t have children, but God had different plans for us. He gave us two beautiful girls. We are super blessed to have them and thank God for them everyday, but we know and they know our family is not complete. We would love to have a total of  4-5 children. We know that the girls will be quite a bit older than our son, but would like to have another boy in about two years. Then if God blesses us with more children another baby two years later would be great! So our next two-three will be closer in age. We have so much love to offer and so do the girls. We have always known since day one we were going to have more children, and the girls have always begged us for more. The timing is now right (Crystal just graduated from college!) and God willing we will be adding to our family very soon.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Adoption Story', 3117, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1341865806, 0),
(849, 'contact us by email at:\n\njamesandmara2adopt@gmail.com', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Email Us', 2835, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1341936656, 0),
