(850, 'We love our pets! We have two mini long haired dachshunds Max and Sady. They are our babies and absolutely love and adore our children. Our cat Hope has been with us our entire marriage. They are great with people especially children and will love the new addition to our family!', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Pets', 3117, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1341946049, 0),
