(864, 'We live in a ranch style house with a daylight basement. The home has 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and a large fenced in back yard. We have relationships with all of our neighbors and enjoy grilling out and each other’s company.  There are children of all ages in our neighborhood and a park within walking distance. We live in an excellent school district and have access to many libraries and recreational facilities.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Home ', 3283, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1342571423, 0),
(865, 'Some special traditions in our family are Nana''s Pajama Party at Christmas, going to the circus, Disney on Ice and our annual kayak and camping trip.  We also celebrate the holidays like everyone else, doing things like pumpkin carving, dressing up for Halloween, hiding Easter eggs and picking out the perfect Christmas tree.  Birthdays are a big deal in our house.  There is always a party with family, friends, food and a lot of laughs. ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Holidays and Traditions', 3283, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1342571603, 0),
(866, 'We both love the water and beach so much that most of our vacations take place around water.  We have been very fortunate to see some of the most beautiful beaches.  We have spent time in the Caribbean, Gulf of Mexico and Jamaica.  We spend at least 1 week in the spring on the Gulf Coast.  We like to take trips to the mountains and weekend getaways whenever we can.  We love exploring new places and can''t wait to share that with your child.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Vacation &amp; Travel', 3283, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1342571641, 0),
(867, 'We adopted Kimchee when she was 5 months old.  She is one of the smartest and definitely the most loyal dogs.  She enjoys long walks on the beach, trips to the park and going for car rides.  She can''t wait to be a big sister.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Kimchee', 3283, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1342571908, 0),
