(871, '<div><span>If you think we are a match for your placement plans, feel free to contact at <span style="color: #006699; font-family: ''trebuchet ms'', geneva; font-size: small;"><strong>800-705-3238</strong> </span> or send us an <a href="mailto:brianandjjadopt@gmail.com" target="blank">email</a>.</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div>If you''d like to speak to an adoption professional about us, call Kim Hines at 804-878-9019 or 800-690-4206</div>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Contact Us', 3315, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1342632250, 0),
(870, 'Thank you again for taking the time to get to know us.  We hope that you have a better sense of who we are, our love for each other and the love we will pour onto your child as they are welcomed into our family.  We promise to always be honest, loving and supportive.  Your child will always know how much you love them.  We look forward to getting to know about your interests and hobbies so that we may one day share them with your child. Know that we are praying for you and your child every day.\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Thank you ', 3283, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1342573799, 0),
