(908, '•We promise to always be honest, loving and supportive. Your child will always know how much you love them. We look forward to getting to know about your interests and hobbies so that we may one day share them with your child. Know that we are praying for you and your child every day.\n•We promise to raise your child in a Christian home with morals, values and responsibilities.\n•We promise to always let your child be themselves and be proud of them no matter what.\n•We promise to tell them and show them each and everyday how much they are loved.\n•We promise to always have a dog.\n•We promise to share our love of art.\n•We promise to read bedtime stories every night.\n•We promise to always show nothing but respect for you and your family.\n•We promise to share our love of new places and cultures with them.\n•We promise that your child will be a part of a large loving family - including grandparents, many aunts and uncles, great-grandparents,and of course cousins to play with.\n•We promise to always tell them the truth.\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Promises to you', 3283, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1343480061, 0),
