(913, 'Here is portion of a reference letter written by Steven''s friend named Paul, which was submitted to the adoption agency: \n\n\nSteven and I became friends as a result of our common interests and values and because of Steven''s positive, friendly nature.  Steven has a tremendous sense of humor, an uncanny ability to respect and empathize with all people, and unbelievable work ethic and a remarkable passion for life.  Steven quickly became one of the most respected employees at the firm as a result of these qualities.  \n\nFrom observing the way Steven and Chris have interacted with my three children over the years, leaves no doubt in my mind they will be amazing parents.  They have a genuine excitement when they are with my children.  Chris is remarkably caring and has an amazing ability to communicate and relate to my kids.  Often shy and reserved, my kids open up with Chris and Steven, as they can feel their sincere warmth, love and gentle nature.  ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Steven ', 3297, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1349562722, 0),
