(915, 'Spencer is a happy, expressive, intelligent five-year-old.  His interests include super heroes (Wolverine is his favorite), fishing, playing outside, puzzles, books, and games of all kind.  He enjoys helping both Mommy and Daddy around the house.  He''s very excited to start Kindergarten in the fall.  While we haven''t talked to him about having another child or the adoption process, he has recently begun to tell us how much he would like to be a big brother.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Spencer', 3281, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1343007680, 0),
