(1546, 'My husband Chris is great with children. He has a fabulous sense of humor, is trustworthy, hard working, and committed.  There is never a dull moment in our home.  He has the ability to make light of difficult situations, bringing a ray of sunshine to each day.  He can be trusted and has a great sense of integrity.  People feel that they can talk with him about anything and the conversation will stay between the two of them.  \n\nChris is committed to his family.  He will drop everything at work to attend special family events.  If there is a dance recital or ball game, Chris will be there to support this little one.  Chris attended public school on Long Island and went on to obtain a BA in Psychology.  After working in the dot com industry for a few years, Chris has a successful career in computer technology.  He works for a small technology firm, which assists companies with their computer issues. \n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Christopher', 6655, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1398010385, 0),
