(1015, '<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;">We both are originally from Italy. Gaia is from "the city". A beautiful and historic city of Italy. Ben is from the country side. From a town surrounded by mountains and wet by the lake. Grown up in two different and complimentary places, our destiny crossed, unexpectedly, for the first time through a common friend when we were in college. After few years of engagement, friendship, and intense studying to complete our degrees, we got married on a cold winter day warmed by great joy and cheers.   <br /></span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;"><br /></span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;">Our new life as a married couple was soon followed by a new adventure. We moved to the United States. Ben had an opportunity to gain a doctoral degree in mechanical engineering.  To leave behind our large families and our friends was not an easy decision; however, the loving community of friends who have welcomed us here have made us more certain of the good path we have taken.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;"><br /></span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;">Soon after Ben graduated, he found an engineering job he really enjoys and which seems to offer a stable and promising prospective to our family, here. Luckily, our extended families really like to travel and whenever possible they come to spend some time with us. Even Gaia''s 91 years old grandmother has already traveled this far to visit us! </span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;"><br /></span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;">Ben is the third of four brothers; the older ones are married with kids. The oldest is a doctor. The second is a lawyer, involved in the academics for a future as a law professor. The youngest is an artist currently working on his master degree in art photography. </span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;"><br /></span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;">Gaia is the only child, but her cousin (married to a basketball coach and with a daughter) is like a sister to her. We have a total of eight nephews and nieces, whom we profoundly love. Their ages go from newborn to 10 years old.  </span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;"><br /></span></p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><span style="color:#0000ff;">Our parents have all recently retired and, as they are still full of energy, they really enjoy spending a lot of time with their grandchildren.</span></p>\n<p> </p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'A bit of our history', 3474, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1353334839, 0),
