(1038, 'Dear Birthmother,\n\nWe want you to know that we will love and care for your child just as if we gave birth to him or her.  It is our prayer that all our children will grow up to love God and to serve Him with all of their heart.  We know you are facing a very hard decision and we want you to know we are praying for you.  Above all else we understand adoption because we have been adopted by God and He has already prepared a place for us in His home.\n\nIn Christ,\nMichael and Rhonda', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Birthmother Letter', 3158, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1349733482, 0),
