(1042, 'John’s Career as a Doctor\n\nI am a physician with a family oriented practice.  My career as a physician has helped us achieve great financial stability, a comfortable living and will allow Diane to be a stay at home mom.  Owning my own practice allows me to set my own schedule so I will be able to have a lot of family time.  \n\nJohn as a Father (written by Diane)\n\nI’ve been lucky enough to experience John’s love every day and watch him with our nieces and nephews.   John is caring, loving, patient and fun.  He will be a very hands on father, involved with changing diapers, doing homework, helping with science projects and planning fun family outings together.  John is an amazing husband and will be an incredible father!\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About John', 3925, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1350344612, 0),
(1043, 'My wife Lacie is one of the most loving, caring people I have ever met. She is always willing to put herself out to take care of me or others. Lacie loves to have fun and is always trying to come up with new and exciting things for us to do.Lacie also encourages me to appreciate the small things in life like spending time together watching a movie or taking a walk around the yard while playing with the dogs.  We have a special relationship with our niece and nephews and when I watch Lacie with them I know she will make the most fantastic mom. ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Lacie', 2230, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1350412227, 0),
