(1058, 'Meet Kiley according to Jerry\n\n\nKiley has a warm, kind, caring, and compassionate soul, one that is tempered with tremendous strength, patience, and determination. She is great fun to be around as well. Everyone she meets and gets to know loves being around her. She is that nice! \n\nPeople are either good with kids or they are not.  I realized early in our relationship that Kiley would be an amazing mother. Whenever she is around children she becomes ever more radiant and the kids absolutely converge on her. It is such a beautiful sight to witness; you can just tell she was meant to be a mother.\n\nShe has a heartwarming affection for animals. Our pets love to snuggle with her, Cooper especially. He’s such a momma’s boy when she’s around.\nI would be remiss if I didn’t mention that she’s a fantastic cook! She also loves to clean; so much so that her family has given her a nickname and they tease her about it. Kiley is a phenomenal woman, and I am blessed to be her husband.\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Kiley', 1679, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1351781965, 0),
