(1411, '<p><span style="font-size:small;">Ron is fun, caring and loving!!!! He works very hard to take care of his family... but he likes to relax and have fun too ;) He loves children and children love him. Our nephews and nieces always want to hang out with him because he is the "hip" uncle.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:small;">I always tell Ron that he must have been a dolphin in his other life because HE LOVES WATER! He enjoys swimming in the ocean and going scuba-diving. He also plays golf and tennis and looks forward to being active and involved with the child we are blessed to raise. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:small;">Ron was born in New Jersey, he studied engineering in college, and now works in a big consulting firm running one of their divisions. He loves what he does and I think he is amazing at it! He is the best husband I could have asked for and I am sure he will be the best dad to the baby who joins our family!!!!!</span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Ron, by Andie', 5875, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1372817367, 0),
