(1093, 'About Patrick: \nI really enjoy reading and learning. I have a degree in Religion and Philosophy.  After taking a few years off from school I attended Seminary where I met Jen. I have continued my education by working on a Doctorate of Ministry program. \n\nJen and I have worked for the past seven years at the school she started. There are few people in this world that you can spend almost all day, every day together and still get along, but Jen and I have for many years now. \n\nI enjoy singing and playing the drums and piano. I am the Pastor of Worship and Administration at church. I also oversee the preschool at our church. \n\nI love Alabama football. Every Saturday during football season Jen, Caden, and I go to my parents house for the game and dinner. \n\nI love being a dad and watching Caden grow and learn new things and look forward to adding another child to our family. \n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Patrick', 2554, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1352057800, 0),
(1094, 'We met while we were both working at a restaurant in 2005. We had an instant friendship that eventually turned into a loving relationship. In 2009, Eric proposed and we were married in September 2010. We enjoy spending our time going to ball games (Go Brewers!), game nights with friends/family, working on our home, playing tennis, playing with our German Shepherd, Harley, and being with our niece and nephews. \n\n​\n \nWe own a three bedroom home, with a large fenced in yard, on a quiet street. We live in a great neighborhood full of young families with children. We get together with neighbors for our annual, neighborhood watch block party. There are two beautiful parks very close to our home\n \n​\n \nThere are many things we are looking forward to doing as a family like, watching Fourth of July fireworks from our backyard, teaching our child to play baseball, exploring the children’s museum, swimming, fishing up north and watching him or her grow and learn; just to name a few!\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'ABOUT US', 4736, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1352066195, 0),
