(1110, 'We are Brennan and Pam and we are very honored that you are taking the time to read our story and get to know us a little more.  What an incredible special person you are to consider adoption for your baby, and to consider us as the adoptive family.  Whatever the outcome may be, we wish you all the best, sincerely from our hearts.\n\nWe have both hoped for a family to grow with and pursuing adoption has made our dream possible. Words can’t express how excited we are to start the journey and become parents.  We plan to talk about your love for them and your decision to place them for adoption was for them to have the best life possible.  We promise to love them and raise them in a Christian home.\n\nFamily is very important to us. We are a fun-loving, outgoing, energetic and happy couple with lots of love to give to a child. We share the same ideas and always support each other and make decisions together. We enjoy spending time together doing activities like taking walks with our dog, going to movies,  dinner parties with friends, and sporting events.  We look forward to doing fun activities in the future as a family.\n\nThank you again for considering us to be parents for your child.  We are so grateful for you and we will continue to pray for you everyday.\n\nBrennan and Pam', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Hopeful adoptive couple', 1434, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1352481735, 0),
