(1145, 'We each have very big extended families too that provide a great net of support. With a total of nine nieces and two nephews, we have a lot of experience caring for and playing with kids. We have babysat for them and seen them grow up. \n\nPatty''s sister lives on a farm and Jim''s family has a cottage on a small lake which allows us to spend vacations with family at these fun spots where there is water sports and horseback riding. But what we like most of all, is spending time with family on holidays. ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our families', 3313, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1353471077, 0),
