(1157, 'Gaia is well described by her name. Gaia is synonym for joy. When she smiles, the room is filled with light.  It was from her smile that our story began. In the ups and downs of life, in the joyful as well as in the sorrowful moments, she has always colored my days with passion and affection.  Being an Italian woman, she enjoys cooking tasty traditional meals (especially when our friends come over)....and using her Italian flavor when it comes to fashion....And now, with these, she gives her best when dealing with our daughter. Normally, it takes very little to figure out who took care of choosing Maria''s cloths for the day :)\nWith Maria, she is a very nurturing mom (she always invests lots of energy and thoughts to meet our daughter needs and curiosity)....many times friends told her she has been made to be a mom.\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'ABOUT GAIA (by Ben)', 3474, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1354225484, 0),
