(1162, 'I am so excited to be a mom!  I have wanted to be a mom ever since I was a little girl.  I want to be a great playmate to my children and have so much fun with them.  I also want to be a teacher to them, to help form their beliefs, morals, and attitudes.  I also want to be a disciplinary as needed.  I want them to grow up knowing right and wrong and choosing right.  I want to help them be the best version of themselves.  \n<br /><br />\nHowever, it is the little day-to-day things I daydream about.  I am so excited for bath time, reading stories, and snuggling.  I cannot wait to bake with them.  Letting them be creative with decorating cookies, or topping homemade pizzas are memories just waiting to be made.  I cannot wait to see their big grins when they get their first "under doggie" on the swing set.  I know being a mom is what I was born to do, and I am so ready to get started.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Excited to be a Mom', 3724, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1354763874, 0),
(1163, 'I truly cannot wait to be a dad.  Sure, I am an adult, mature, and all that good stuff, but I am really just a big kid.  I am so darn excited to play games, play with toys, and do so many fun things with my children.  On a more serious note, I am most excited to impart knowledge to them, from how the world works, to learning about faith.  I also cannot wait to help teach them coordination and how to work with others in team sports.  My favorite thing when spending time with children is that look of "no way, that is so cool."  I hope to share my desire to make a positive difference in the world. I will always be there to encourage their passions in every aspect of life.  I am also excited to see their interests and hopefully gain new interests through them.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Eager to be a dad', 3724, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1354763977, 0),
