(1458, 'Our friends all share in our joy and excitement at becoming parents. All of them have young children, so playmates will never be in short supply!\n\n\n\n\nBoth sets of parents live close by as well. We see them often and enjoy the time we spend together. Family means everything to us! Our parents can''t wait to be grandparents.\n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Friends and Family', 4663, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1377747735, 0),
