(1231, 'Shia is a Black German Shepard who we rescued from the local animal shelter 2 years ago. She is active and loves to play ball outside, swim in her pool, loves the lake and both and enjoys playing in the snow! She is watchful of her little sisters and likes to play tug of war with Bella whenever she can get Bella to play.\n\n\n\nBella is a black chihuahua mix who we rescued from the pound 4 years ago. She is playful, likes to play ball, loves to cuddle, snuggle and be loved. Bella enjoys being outside in the summer time but doesn''t enjoy the winter as much.\n\n\n\nYama is a brindle chihuahua who Kerri got 6 years ago. Yama is small and would sleep all day if we let her. Yama is cold even in the warm weather. She enjoys laying in the sun in the Summer and would rather not go outside in the Winter. She likes to be bundled up in the winter.  Yama loves to snuggle and be wrapped up in a blanket.\n \n\n\nAll 3 will be very accepting of a child in the home and they can''t wait for a new addition to the family!!', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Shia Bella and Yama', 4942, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1369081917, 0),
