(1241, 'We enjoy traveling around the country and around the world! We have visited India, London, and Malaysia. It will be a blast to take our child on trips and see which cultures and cuisines they enjoy the most. We stay physically active and love being outside biking, hiking, and playing tennis. \n\n\nWe’re eagerly awaiting the time we can take our child on their first bike ride or teach them how to serve a tennis ball! When we’re not outside, we sharpen our skills at Rock Band or cheer for our favorites on American Idol.\n\n\nWe also love to read and are looking forward to snuggling up with our child to read Goodnight Moon for the 12th time in a row! Our dog, Mia, is going to love having a new playmate to throw the ball for a fun game of fetch.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Interests', 5240, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1361742104, 0),
