(1242, 'We are very proud and honored to tell our love story and wanted to provide some details to you.  We met when I was 16 and Steve was 19 working at a local swimming pool.  For a year we were only co-workers and friend.  A deep true friendship began blossoming into something beyond our dreams.  We fell into love and dated seriously until I was a Freshman in College.  At this point we needed to take a break.  And what a break it was...about 18 years before we would reunite.  Over the many years apart we kept in touch every so often and would run into each at the local mall but the timing never seemed right for us.  Long story short (the long version is really cool!) we finally did reunite and now more than ever I do believe God has a plan on his terms when your dreams will come true.  My dreams started coming true the day Steve and I got back together and started planning the rest of our life.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Steve and Lisa&#039;s Love Story', 5155, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1361403103, 0),
(1243, ' I am "expecting" and this is a most wonderful time, a time to treasure! True there are no changes going on in my body, no hormones out of whack, no mood swings (other than the normal lol) but I still dream and plan and hope for a bright and happy future for my baby just like every expectant mother. I try to picture in my mind what he/she will look like and imagine the sound of baby laughter in the house. Of bruised knees and bed time stories, of saying a prayer right before bedtime.\n\n I am "expecting" and expectant mothers have to wait around 40 weeks for their baby to be nurtured in their bellies. My baby''s nurturing is happening in another woman''s belly, a woman that loves that baby enough to want for it a better life than what she can offer. God will have His hand on this baby that comes to us and He will have also nurtured it as He does all children.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Thoughts', 5153, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1361678836, 0),
