(1288, 'We are Lori and Goran Pesic.  We look forward to meeting you to learn more about you and the hopes and dreams you have for your child.  We are thrilled to become parents, and we promise to nurture and guide your baby so that he or she can grow to be responsible, caring, and happy individual.  We are very excited that you are considering becoming a part of our lives, and hope we can take this journey with you.\nPeace and Love To You,\nLori and Goran', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'To A Very Special Person', 1538, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1365261399, 0),
(1289, 'We met in college and started a strong foundation as friends.  We quickly fell in love and realized we were meant to spend the rest of our lives together.  We''ve been happily married for 14 years and have always dreamed of having a home filled with laughter and the joy of children.  We can''t wait to watch the cartoon network, hide Easter baskets and even change diapers.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Us', 1538, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1365463146, 0),
(1290, 'Lori is my best friend and soul mate.  She has such a big heart and everyone that meets her is drawn to her friendly and warm personality.  She is a dedicated art teacher and enjoys volunteering at arts and crafts nights, prom decorating, and cooking yummy meals for us.  She is thrilled about having a child to bake cookies together and play games with at night.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Lori by Goran', 1538, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1365265649, 0),
