(1286, '\nLooking Forward to Parenthood\n \nOpen-minded, curious, adventurous, and responsible people, we really want to share all the love \nwe have with a child.  We believe the best way to teach values like honesty, tolerance, and self-\nconfidence to our child is to live them ourselves.  It is also important to provide affection, stability,\nand lots of encouragement.  We can''t wait to be parents and examine caterpillars up close, \nleave cookies for Santa, give basketball lessons, finger-paint with wild colors, and end \neach day with a bedtime story.  We''re excited about taking turns staying home with our baby.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Ready to be a Family', 1538, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1365260606, 0),
