(1263, 'Scot and Lindsay were married in the fall of 2002. Scot is currently in Operations Management, and Lindsay is employed with all the affairs of the home. They have two biological children, Reagan (7) and Lilli (4). They live in a rural setting in NE Ohio. The family attends and is involved in a local non-denominational church. Their involvement includes: worship band, bible studies, small groups, etc. ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Scot and Lindsay', 3150, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1363788512, 0),
(1264, 'Reagan is 7, enjoys being outside, playing basketball and Legos. Lilli is 4 and loves all babies, all animals and singing. We have had the privilege of raising some farm animals over the years, chickens and cows.  We have a 9 year old lab mix dog, Kayah, and she is the best dog you could ask for. \nOur house is on a rural street, surrounded by 4 acres with more grass and woods than any child could ever want. The house is over 80 years old, but has been updated over the years.  \n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About our Kids/Home', 3150, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1363797430, 0),
