(1315, '<p><em><span style="font-family:georgia, palatino;font-size:small;">~ First and foremost, we promise your child <strong>love &amp; affection</strong> -- from us, our extended family, and our friends.</span></em><em></em><br /><em><span style="font-family:georgia, palatino;font-size:small;">~ We will do our best to ensure his or her <strong>safety/security</strong>, which is the basis of developing confidence and independence.</span></em> <em></em><br /><em><span style="font-family:georgia, palatino;font-size:small;">~ We will be a <strong>guiding </strong>force in her/his life, without being  domineering or overly controlling. Everyone should feel free to be who  they really are.</span></em><em></em><br /><em><span style="font-family:georgia, palatino;font-size:small;">~ We will teach and demonstrate a <strong>healthy lifestyle </strong>-- this is a day-to-day focus of our parenting style.</span></em><em></em><br /><em><span style="font-family:georgia, palatino;font-size:small;">~ We will ensure that our kids get an <strong>excellent education</strong>, through providing opportunities but also nurturing a true love of learning -- and  a sense of the importance of hard work.</span></em><em></em><br /><em><span style="font-family:georgia, palatino;font-size:small;">~ We will show him or her many different ways to <strong>celebrate life</strong> --  on big festive occasions but also in small quiet moments. Smiles,   fun,  and a variety of enjoyable experiences are as important as   anything in  life, not to be skimped on...</span></em><em></em><br /><em><span style="font-family:georgia, palatino;font-size:small;">~ We will give your child the<strong> time and attention</strong> every child needs in order to feel TRULY VALUED and to learn to value others.</span></em></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Adoption Pledge', 5253, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1367496482, 0),
