(1320, '<img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/joeandstacy/Photos/Stacy.JPG" alt="Stacy" width="200" align="left">\nAbout Stacy:\nI am a quiet person until I get to know you and then I become more outgoing.  I am smart and am a good listener.  I am a happy person and tend to think positively.  I have a good sense of humor and enjoy having fun.  I am a person of faith and have good morals. \n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/joeandstacy/Photos/Joe.JPG" alt="Joe" width="200" align="left">\nAbout Joe:\nI’m relatively outgoing, especially in groups of friends. I like to make jokes and be silly, but I can be serious too, and my friends know that they can come to me for a respectful conversation. I am an optimist, if I’m sad about anything, it won’t stay with me long. I just like to be happy too much.\n<br>\n<br>\nTo really get to know us, you should look at our portfolio as it documents our lives from early childhood until now.  It really displays our personalities.  We hope you enjoy it!', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Us', 5727, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1368764852, 0),
