(1421, '<p style="text-align: justify;">We''ve created a profile book to share more about ourselves.&nbsp; You can use the "Print Profile" button at the top right of the page to download and save a 54 MB PDF for offline viewing or printing.&nbsp; You can also click on the link to immediately view a lower resolution version:</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://app.picaboo.com/WebView/Project.aspx?clientID=d62c677d193841a4cd2cebc71a8e125a&amp;version=285191&amp;siteID=ViaPreview">Profile Photo Book</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">You can also view online versions of Jacob''s update books. &nbsp;These versions have had the name of Jacob''s birthmother and siblings removed, as well as the messages of a more personal nature. &nbsp;They serve as an extension of our profile, giving you more insight into our family and our journey as parents.</p><p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span><a href="http://app.picaboo.com/WebView/Project.aspx?clientID=ac1549427304da30daec8a6758344ee4&amp;version=217337&amp;siteID=ViaPreview" target="_blank">Update 1</a></span></p>\n<p><span><a href="http://app.picaboo.com/WebView/Project.aspx?clientID=d92f0f60eb924a5528905202edf040b1&amp;version=217338&amp;siteID=ViaPreview" target="_blank">Update 2</a></span></p>\n<p><span><a href="http://app.picaboo.com/WebView/Project.aspx?clientID=1bdc36622b9b352d09b452061cae512f&amp;version=217342&amp;siteID=ViaPreview" target="_blank">Update 3</a></span></p>\n<p><span><a href="http://app.picaboo.com/WebView/Project.aspx?clientID=e1d376d2c7316862c58a307df71cd0c3&amp;version=242627&amp;siteID=ViaPreview" target="_blank">Update 4</a></span></p>\n<p><span><a href="http://app.picaboo.com/WebView/Project.aspx?clientID=faa84c9745de2267b1b23db449296f2a&amp;version=269907&amp;siteID=ViaPreview" target="_blank">Update 5</a></span></p>\n<p><span><a href="http://app.picaboo.com/WebView/Project.aspx?clientID=3bff1df1fa4ef95539c9fe9bf075ed31&amp;version=297924&amp;siteID=ViaPreview" target="_blank">Update 6</a></span></p>\n<p><span><a href="http://app.picaboo.com/WebView/Project.aspx?clientID=d33bec113c28047d025a1fed1b8a92eb&amp;version=324974&amp;siteID=ViaPreview" target="_blank">Update 7</a></span></p>\n<p><span><a href="http://app.picaboo.com/WebView/Project.aspx?clientID=c6c4429fe85f8264229bbc08be78014a&amp;version=345789&amp;siteID=ViaPreview" target="_blank">Update 8</a></span></p>\n<p><span><a href="http://app.picaboo.com/WebView/Project.aspx?clientID=1446e3a58191574a959290ae931f369a&version=371963&siteID=ViaPreview\n" target="_blank">Update 9</a></span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Profile Book', 2525, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1381112710, 0),
