(1340, '<p> </p>\n<p><em><strong> <img style="float:left;" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/m/photos/get_image/original/8264937b65f9dba3a6a7ecd8520923b2.jpg" alt="Stacy" width="195" height="130" /></strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>About Stacy:</strong></em> I am a quiet person until I get to know you and then I become more  outgoing.  I am smart and am a good listener.  I am a happy person and  tend to think positively.  I have a good sense of humor and enjoy having  fun.  I am a person of faith and have good morals.  <br /><br /></p>\n<p><br /><br /><br /><br /><img title="Joe" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/joeandstacy/Photos/Joe.jpg" alt="Joe" width="133" height="200" align="left" /><strong><em> </em></strong></p>\n<p><strong><em>About Joe:</em></strong> I’m relatively outgoing, especially in groups of friends. I like to make  jokes and be silly, but I can be serious too, and my friends know that  they can come to me for a respectful conversation. I am an optimist, if  I’m sad about anything, it won’t stay with me long. I just like to be  happy too much.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img style="float:left;" title="Lucas" src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/joeandstacy/Photos/IMG_4780_sm.JPG" alt="Lucas" width="137" height="203" /><strong> </strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>About Lucas:</strong> Hi I''m Lucas!  I am currently an only child but I can''t wait for a younger sibling to play with and love.  I am a happy little boy full of giggles and smiles.  I am definitely the center of my parent''s world!  I give hugs and kisses and I love to play and learn new things!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>To really get to know us, you should look at <a href="http://www.parentfinder.com/profileflipbook/5727-joeandstacy/5727-joeandstacy.html" target="_blank">our portfolio</a> as it  documents our lives from early childhood until now.  It really displays  our personalities.  We hope you enjoy it!</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Us', 5727, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1409023324, 0),
(1341, '<p>                                                            <img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/LoriandSam/407733_10151465729093998_2059693171_n.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="200" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Ellarose is our five year old daughter.  She enjoys going swimming, playing soccer and dancing.  Ellarose also loves traveling to Disney World, dressing up, having playdates with her cousins and friends, and playing with dolls.  She goes to school and will attend Kindergarten in September.  Ellarose cannot wait to be a big sister and promises to "feed and hold the baby!"  </p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Daughter', 5699, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1369184560, 0),
