(1343, 'My life is a very active one, full of adventures that are fun for children and grownups to do together.       \n\n\n\nAs a very family-oriented person, I enjoy going with my family and friends on outings to nearby zoos, parks, lakes, festivals, and pools.   I also enjoy traveling as much as I can.  I love go to beaches, the mountains, the islands, and Europe.  \n\n \nI tend to get involved in a variety of volunteer activities too.  I''ve really enjoyed teaching english as a second language, leading self-esteem seminars, serving as a camp counselor, tutoring, and delivering meals to the homeless. \n\nRather than watching sports, I like participating in them.  Racquetball, biking, and hiking are my favorites.  \n\nWhen I''m not up and around, I love to read novels and play board games.  \n\n\n \n\n\n \n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Interests and Hobbies', 5686, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1408878291, 0),
