(1393, 'We have been doing lots of research regarding adoption and through that research, we have come across many blogs posted by birth mothers or first mothers that detail their adoption experience (if you are interested, we would be glad to provide you with some links).  Please know that we are firm believers that BEST place for your baby to be is with you, his mother.  There are many resources available to you and your family to aid you in raising your child.  That being said, if these resources have been researched and all options have been explored and you feel that there is no way that you would be able to raise your baby, if you feel that adoption or abortion are truly your only options, then please choose life for your baby and please consider us as a new/second family for your baby.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Food for thought...', 5853, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1371912895, 0),
