(1412, '<p><span style="font-size:small;">Andie is the most amazing person I have ever met. We fell in love quickly and have been ever since! What makes her amazing is her heart: she cares and loves like no one else. She is the oldest of three girls and so has had a maternal nature her entire life. She will protect the child with every bit of her being.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:small;"> </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:small;">Andie is from Argentina and had lived there until we got married 12 years ago. She speaks Spanish and English and a little of Portuguese and Italian, all of which she will share with a child. Andie is big on education: she loves to read and is constantly learning new things. She studied computer science in college and has a master''s degree. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:small;"> </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:small;">When I see Andie smile, it touches my heart. I know she will make a great mom!!!</span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Andie, by Ron', 5875, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1372816885, 0),
(1413, 'Four years ago we were blessed when we had Zoe and Millie joined our family!!! They are both Havanese, which is a very small breed. We call them Pompis because they look like pomp-pons.\n\n\nAndie has been training the doggies since they were six months old. They are very well behaved and love playing with children!!!\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Doggies', 5875, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1372819786, 0),
