(1440, '<p style="text-align:justify;">Jacob''s heritage is Caucasian-Hispanic, as his birthfather is from El Salvador.  He''s tall for his age and has a very good appetite.  He has curly hair that everyone loves.  His favorite foods include apples and applesauce, cheese, chicken, raisins, grapes, tomatoes, and guacamole.  He doesn''t like sweets and won''t eat ice cream, cookies, cake, or chocolate milk. He loves playing outside and in water.  His favorite things to play with are cars, trucks, trains, blocks, and alphabet magnets.  His favorite shows are The Backyardigans, Dinosaur Train, and Super Why, and his favorite movies are Cars, Up, and Lion King.  He loves reading and enjoys going through several books before going to bed.  He''s a very happy child and laughs easily.</p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Jacob', 2525, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1401848849, 0),
