(1456, 'Thank you for considering us. \n\nIf you would like to know more about us, we would love to chat with you. You can reach us through the following ways:<br>\n\n♥ Call our agency, Adoption Connection at 1-800-972-9225, and ask about Ian and Nick<br>\n\n♥ Call us directly at 1-888-444-9498<br>\n\n♥ email us at: larocque.hart@gmail.com<br>\n\n♥ text us at 510-847-1981<br>\n\nThanks!\n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Contact Us!', 6131, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1376945421, 0),
(1471, '<p><strong><span style="font-family:''book antiqua'', palatino;font-size:small;"> </span></strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:''book antiqua'', palatino;font-size:small;">We met 6 years ago through some friends of ours and have been married for the last 4 years.  We love our life together and enjoy the time we spend together.  We love being outdoors fishing, camping and boating.  We enjoy playing games, spending time with friends and family, playing with our dogs, gardening and traveling to new places when we can.  During the winter we love to watch football in person or on TV, particularly the Denver Broncos or Miami Dolphins.  </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:''book antiqua'', palatino;font-size:small;"> </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:''book antiqua'', palatino;font-size:small;"><span>We are a loving couple who is fortunate to enjoy financial stability and lots of time to enjoy the moments that make life special.  Our life together is filled with family, friends and lots of fun activity, all of which we are ready to share with a child.  We love getting out and being active, whether it is a day of fishing at the lake or an evening walk.  We have a garden in our backyard and we look forward to seeing a little one enjoy playing in the dirt as he or she helps pick veggies we have grown ourselves.  We love getting together with family for backyard BBQ''s and big holiday celebrations, both of our families are excited to welcome their newest member to the family.  Whether it is doing homework, enjoying dinner together every night or rooting him or her on in their chosen hobby, if we are chosen we will be there with lots of love and a lifetime of support.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:''book antiqua'', palatino;font-size:small;"> </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:''book antiqua'', palatino;font-size:small;"> </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:''book antiqua'', palatino;font-size:small;">We have 3 dogs; Shia who is a german Shephard, and Yama and Bella who are mixed chihuahuas, all of which are wonderful with children.  Our life is not yet complete, we want to be parents.  We have been trying to have a child naturally since we got married and have been unsuccessful.  We have had infertility and two pregnancies that ended in a miscarriage during these 4 years.  Although we were devistated with the news of our infertility and both miscarriages, we have found through our failed attempts that we have become stronger as a couple.  We realize we are meant to have a child through adoption, a path that God has led us down and we are very excited about this journey and can''t wait to be a part of it.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:''book antiqua'', palatino;font-size:small;"> </span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Us', 4942, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1381976450, 0),
(1457, 'Please click <a href=http://www.parentfinder.com/profileflipbook/6175-jennyandshawna/6175-jennyandshawna.html target= _blank>here</a> to view Jenny and Shawna ''s profile flip book', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'E-book Profile', 6175, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1377535796, 1),
(1459, '1. We will faithfully make it our mission to teach you about God and expose you to the beliefs of others so that you may grow up to love, respect, and tolerate all people.\n\n\n\n2. We will surround you with a  large group of family and friends who will envelop you with their love.\n\n\n\n3.  We will always be there to protect you; pick you up when you stumble, catch you when you fall and wipe away your tears and fears with words of comfort and support.\n\n\n\n4. We will guide you through the wonders of life, teach you right from wrong and give you values and traditions that will enable you to grow into your fullest potential and beyond.\n\n\n\n5. We will strive to instill in you a sense of pride and accomplishment, a feeling of self-worth and knowledge of your priceless worth in our lives.\n\n\n\n6. We will give you the best educational opportunities you desire; not only in the classroom but also in the real world.\n\n\n\n7. We promise to support and encourage each and every career choice and life adventure you choose.\n\n\n\n8. We will always encourage your dreams. There will never be a time that you doubt your abilities to be who you want to be.\n\n\n\n9. We will endeavour to see the world through your eyes and to remain young at heart.\n\n\n\n10. We will strive each and every minute to give you a happy home filled with unconditional love. We will make sure you know the history of who you are and where you came from; and we promise to be there for you every step of the way as you become the person you were meant to be.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '10 Promises to Our Chosen Child', 4663, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1377746667, 0),
(1460, 'Thank you for taking the time to get to know us. We promise to provide a home full of laughter and fun that is balanced with boundaries and guidance and lots and lots of LOVE!', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Thank You!', 4663, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1377744854, 0),
