(1514, '<table>\n<tr>\n<td><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/jmorahan/2014Hayley.jpg" height="120"></td>\n<td>\nHayley was born in April of 2011 in Cleveland, OH and has been our daughter since she was 6 days old.   Hayley is very tiny for her age, but she is a very energetic and social little girl who talks non-stop and is looking forward to being a “big sister”!  She loves singing, dancing, swimming, tumbling, reading stories, building with legos, and playing outside.  We admire her strong-willed personality but definitely admit that some days it gives us quite the parenting challenge :-)</td>\n</tr>\n</table>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Hayley', 6566, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1394079224, 0),
