(1516, 'We Promise:\n\nTo instill in your child a deep appreciation for you and a genuine understanding of how much you love her; to shower your child with love, affection, humor, understanding, and encouragement; to teach your child the wonders of learning and encourage creativity and imagination, exposing her to books, music, dance, arts, and sports; to raise your child with a positive outlook on life; to guide and nurture your child to become her own unique, talented self; to foster a genuine regard for God and His creation, and a deep appreciation for all life.\n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Parenting Pledge', 6547, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1393827046, 0),
(1517, '<ul>\n<li>We are a very active family and love to get outdoors for activities such as family bike rides and hikes. </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Our families and friends are very supportive of our decision to adopt.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Julie’s parents live just 20 minutes away from us, and they help us out with babysitting when they can.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ernest’s parents live in Alaska, but they are retired and visit us frequently.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>We are frequent visitors to kid friendly places such as the children''s museum, the butterfly pavilion, and the zoo.  We also have many friends with kids that we like to get together with for play dates.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>We enjoy traveling throughout the year and have recently been to Alaska, San Francisco, and Disney World as a family.</li>\n</ul>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Facts About Our Family', 6566, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1399686288, 0),
(1518, '<table>\n<tr>\n<td><img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/jmorahan/cross.png" width="128" align="center"></td>\n\n<td>We were both raised as Catholics and actively practice our faith.  We were married in the Catholic church and traveled to Italy on our honeymoon where we had our marriage blessed by the Pope.  We attend Mass regularly on Sundays as a family and will do our best to raise our children in the faith.</td>\n</tr>\n</table>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'About Our Faith', 6566, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1394077734, 0),
(1519, '<table>\n<tr>\n\n<td>Since we are both software developers, it makes sense that we turned to online dating to find each other.  We met on e-Harmony and fell in love after our first "blind date" when we agreed to meet in person.  We immediately bonded over our love of the outdoors (camping, hiking, and cycling together), attending sporting events (baseball and football games), traveling, and our Catholic faith.  I knew with how patient and caring Ernest was with me, he was going to make a great Dad someday.\n\n<br/><br />\n\nOur personalities complement each other well.  Julie is goal-oriented and driven, and Ernest is easy-going and laid back.  We think combining these personalities together brings out the best of both sides and makes us a strong couple.\n\n<br/><br/>\n\nWe have now been married for over 6 years and remain deeply committed to each other and our marriage vows.  We feel very fortunate that we both had the opportunity to grow up in stable, two-parent homes and have learned much from our own parents about the commitment and love that are required to raise a family.  We want to give our children the same opportunity to grow up in a safe, loving environment.\n</td>\n<td>\n<img src="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/jmorahan/IMG_0492.jpg" width="200"/>\n<i>Gondola Ride in Venice, Italy</i>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Us As a Couple', 6566, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1396907680, 0),
