(1554, '<p><span style="background-color:#ffffff;font-family:''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;font-size:small;color:#000000;">We met in church when I was 13 and James was 15. We started a relationship 2 years later and have been together ever since. Growing up together from a young age gave us time to nurture a close friendship which only grew as we got older. When we decided to marry in March of 2004 we could honestly say we were marrying our best friend, and after 15 years there is no one we would rather be with than each other</span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'How We Met', 6409, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1401994618, 0),
(1555, '<p><span style="font-family:''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;font-size:small;">We are Home Study approved through Keane Center for adoption in Michigan. </span><br /><span style="font-family:''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;font-size:small;">They can assist both us and you in our adoption process and in any state. Thank you </span><br /><span style="font-family:''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;font-size:small;">Contact: Chris Brail: 313-277-4664</span><br /><span style="font-family:''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;font-size:small;"><a href="http://www.keaneadoption.org/">http://www.keaneadoption.org/</a></span><br /><span style="font-family:''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;font-size:small;">Our Email: <a href="mailto:ajadopt32@gmail.com">ajadopt32@gmail.com</a></span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Adoption Center and Contact information ', 6409, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1400691712, 0),
(1556, '<p><span style="color:#5391ac;font-family:''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;font-size:small;">*James: As we are looking to be matched with a son I am going to continue to live my life to be a good example to him and help guide him to be a loving husband, provider, a man of his word, loyal to friends and family, treat others with respect, work hard, and most of all to love God.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;font-size:small;color:#5391ac;">*Angela: I have always known I wanted to be a mother and will care for him with lots of love and thankfulness that I have been given such a precious gift. You will forever have a special place in my heart for the blessing you will be giving us of parenthood and a son. <br /></span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Parenting goals and dreams ', 6409, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1400859239, 0),
(1567, '<p><span style="font-family:''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;font-size:small;">Thank you for taking time to review our profile and getting to know us a little through our page. We know you have big decisions to make and we have already started praying for you and your family as you are considering adoption.  For us adoption was a calling placed on our hearts even in the early years of our relationship as James was adopted when he was 3 months old.  We will be able to offer a unique experience to a child growing up in our home with James being adopted himself. When we were younger we never knew at what point we would adopt but the calling has been made clear to us and we are pursing this path to parenthood whole heartedly.  We are very excited to become first time parents to a son and provide a safe, loving environment for him to grow up in; we are just waiting for our special match.<br />Please know we are grateful for you! </span></p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'To Someone Special ', 6409, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1402024053, 0),
