(1557, 'We would like to thank you for reviewing and reading our profile. We are grateful and honored that you are taking the time to get to know us through our page. We know you have a big decision to make in choosing adoptive parents and we have already started praying for you and your family.\nWe would love the opportunity to parent a son and provide a safe, loving environment for him to grow up in.\nAdoption was a calling placed on our hearts even in the early years of our relationship as James was adopted when he was 3 months old. We will be able to offer a unique experience to a child growing up in our home with James being adopted himself. We are very excited to become first time parents and start our adoption journey!\n\n\nAgency info: Keane Center for Adoption\n(313) 277-4664 Chris Brail', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'To Someone Special: ', 6409, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1400545330, 0),
