(1601, '<p>Thank you for taking the time to learn more about us.  We hope that you feel like you''ve gotten to know us better.  Adoption is the most generous gift anyone could receive.  Should you choose us, we would be forever grateful for your generous gift.  We are so excited about the possibility of adoption and adding to our family and would be honored if chosen.  We pray that you make a decision you are at peace with.  </p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Thank You', 6818, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1406691139, 0),
(1602, '<div></div>\n<table border="0" align="center"><tbody><tr><td style="border:1px solid #990099;" align="center" valign="top"><strong>Gaia''s</strong></td>\n<td style="border:1px solid #000000;background-color:#000000;"> </td>\n<td style="border:1px solid #0000ff;" align="center" valign="top"><strong>Ben''s</strong></td>\n</tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #990099;" align="center" valign="top">I don''t like to iron!!<br /></td>\n<td style="border:1px solid #000000;background-color:#000000;"> </td>\n<td style="border:1px solid #0000ff;" align="center" valign="top">I don''t like sweet potatos</td>\n</tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #990099;" align="center" valign="top">To rush and not enjoy breakfast...<br /></td>\n<td style="border:1px solid #000000;background-color:#000000;"> </td>\n<td style="border:1px solid #0000ff;" align="center" valign="top">To be late</td>\n</tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #990099;" align="center" valign="top">...when it rains or is too cold<br /></td>\n<td style="border:1px solid #000000;background-color:#000000;"> </td>\n<td style="border:1px solid #0000ff;" align="center" valign="top"><span>Too much A/C during summer </span></td>\n</tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #990099;" align="center" valign="top"><br /></td>\n<td style="border:1px solid #000000;background-color:#000000;"> </td>\n<td style="border:1px solid #0000ff;" align="center" valign="top"> </td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p> </p>', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Ben and Gaia&#039;s Dislikes', 3474, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1407172677, 0),
(1603, '<p>Please click <a href="http://www.parentfinder.com/media/users/DanSarahAdopt/DASC_Profile_Book.pdf">here</a> to view Sarah and Daniel''s profile flip book</p>', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'E-book Profile', 6721, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'text', 1409097530, 1),
(1604, 'We hope this letter will give you a sense of who we are as a family and the values and traditions which are important to us.  We are extremely excited to become parents and are grateful to you for helping make that dream a reality.  We look forward to meeting you, welcoming you and your child into our lives and hope to hear from you soon!\n\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Introduction', 6651, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1409445847, 0),
(1605, 'We love living in Brentwood, a family friendly neighborhood just north of Santa Monica, with lots of shops and restaurants within walking distance (especially our favorite, Yogurtland!).  We enjoy walking to the farmer’s market on Sunday mornings and look forward to the day when our child can taste the delicious free samples and play on the playground with the other neighborhood kids.  We also live close to the beach and the popular Third Street Promenade and do our best to take advantage of all of the great things Los Angeles has to offer.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Neighborhood', 6651, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1409445801, 0),
(1606, 'Whether it is going for a walk around our neighborhood or hiking in the local mountains, we like to take advantage of the beautiful Southern California weather and spend time outdoors.  We love to travel and explore new places and look forward to hearing our child ask from the back seat of the car, “are we there yet!?”\n\nBrian’s family loves karaoke and although Carrie was hesitant at first, we are now both officially karaoke rock stars.  We can’t wait to sing the entire Disney songbook with our child!\n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Hobbies and Interests', 6651, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1409445817, 0),
(1607, 'Growing up, we were always supported and loved for who we were and we promise to do the same for our child.  We will help our child find his or her passions and celebrate the things that bring him or her happiness.  \n\nYou will be an important part of our family’s story and we look forward to welcoming you into our family with love and support.  We have chosen open adoption because we want this letter to be just the beginning of a long an open relationship.  We loom forward to talking with you and taking the next step on this journey.  \n', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Promise', 6651, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1409445861, 0),
(1608, 'We grew up in the Midwest, but our careers brought us to the west coast.  Even though the trip from California to Ohio is long, it’s something we believe in doing several times a year so we can see our families and spend quality time together.  We both grew up in large, extended families who are now thrilled to welcome our new family member and they will be coming to California a lot more frequently.  \n\nWe are lucky to live fifteen minutes away from Carrie’s cousin and her family, who we spend time with several times a month.  Their children are extremely excited to have a new cousin nearby to play with and have already shared much of their old baby stuff!  \n\nWe also look forward to visits with Carrie’s brother and his wife, in the San Francisco Bay Area, as they can hardly wait to show their niece or nephew all of the exciting things that Northern California has to offer.  ', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Our Family', 6651, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1409445908, 0),
(1609, 'Kerriann enjoys reading, writing, running, yoga, and soccer.  She loves the outdoors, and she is happiest when spending time with her family and her friends.', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'ABOUT KERRIANN', 6694, 3, 'non,memb', 1, 0, 'html', 1409696504, 0);
